#+TITLE: Leadership Styles
#+AUTHOR: Daniel

There are masculine leadership styles -- aggressive, assertive --, and feminine leadership styles -- interpersonal.

If your style doesn't match the expectations of your style, your effectiveness as a leader diminishes.

Corporate culture is very important.

Ralph has to act with a masculine leadership style, because otherwise, his leadership skills disappear.

The culture that he set up isn't very good -- there's no reward / motivation for the followers.
